headline: Why Shares of Motorola Solutions Sank Today
summary: Motorola's first-quarter results were met by a harsh reaction from the market.  Ultimately, while short-term troubles may persist, Motorola's mission-critical products will help it battle volatility.  Shares of public safety technology provider Motorola Solutions (NYSE: MSI) were down 7% as of 12:45 p.m. ET on Friday.
